325
00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:39,083
You're right,
I can only be me...!

326
00:19:39,166 --> 00:19:40,625
And I accept that!

327
00:19:40,708 --> 00:19:42,250
That was well put, Silvia...

328
00:19:42,333 --> 00:19:43,791
