have reached full capacity!

331
00:19:50,583 --> 00:19:51,916
Merge One!

332
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,791
Merge Two!

333
00:19:53,875 --> 00:19:57,041
Go, Aquarion!

334
00:20:00,375 --> 00:20:03,583
This merge, it's different.

335
00:20:03,666 --> 00:20:05,000
It's incredible!

336
00:20:05,083 --> 00:20:07,541
