338
00:20:16,333 --> 00:20:18,041
It's radiating!

339
00:20:19,125 --> 00:20:21,208
The time has come.

340
00:20:21,291 --> 00:20:23,208
Hey, copycat...!

341
00:20:23,291 --> 00:20:25,000
Can you do this?!

342
00:20:31,375 --> 00:20:32,291
Aquarion!

343
00:20:32,375 --> 00:20:33,333
It's growing!

344
00:20:33,416 --> 00:20:34,833
