345
00:20:34,916 --> 00:20:36,250
Solar diagnostic.

346
00:20:36,333 --> 00:20:38,750
Quantum energy
levels increasing...!

347
00:20:38,833 --> 00:20:42,166
It seems to be
drawing mass from within!

348
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:43,208
