352
00:20:57,333 --> 00:20:58,875
But if they choose
their own course

353
00:20:58,958 --> 00:21:00,583
and respect each other's path...

354
00:21:00,666 --> 00:21:02,833
If they appreciate their
individual strengths,

355
00:21:02,916 --> 00:21:04,708
