356
00:21:04,791 --> 00:21:08,125
But if each arrow faces off
in their own random direction...

357
00:21:08,208 --> 00:21:11,041
Won't they be rendered useless?

358
00:21:11,375 --> 00:21:13,458
Of course, if the
directions were random...

359
00:21:13,541 --> 00:21:15,541
Although... if they're
able to find a connection

360
00:21:15,625 --> 00:21:17,291
