managed to do this...

372
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:46,583
They will transcend
the third dimension...

373
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:50,833
Transcend your configuration
and join as one...

374
00:21:50,916 --> 00:21:53,666
Become a single giant shape!

375
00:22:01,166 --> 00:22:02,458
Mimic that.

376
00:22:02,541 --> 00:22:03,833
The power within
us can never be

377
00:22:03,916 --> 00:22:06,958
duplicated through
pale imitation.

378
00:22:07,041 --> 00:22:07,541
