379
00:22:07,625 --> 00:22:08,375
United...

380
00:22:08,458 --> 00:22:09,750
Trans-dimensional...

381
00:22:09,833 --> 00:22:11,666
Attack!

382
00:22:43,166 --> 00:22:45,291
